{% set title = "Customers — Superviz.io" %}
{% set description = "See how engineering teams at Airbus, Thales, OVHcloud, and more use Superviz.io to monitor infrastructure and reduce incidents." %}
{% set canonical = "https://superviz.io/customers" %}
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
    <section class="page-header">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="badge">Customer Stories</span>
        <h1 style="margin-top: var(--space-4)">
          Trusted by teams that<br /><span class="text-gradient"
            >can't afford downtime</span
          >
        </h1>
        <p class="subtitle subtitle-wide" style="margin-top: var(--space-4)">
          From startups to Fortune 500, engineering teams choose Superviz.io for
          real-time visibility and faster incident response.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="logos-section" style="padding: var(--space-12) 0">
      <div class="container text-center">
        <p
          style="
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: var(--text-sm);
            margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            font-weight: 600;
          "
        >
          Companies monitoring with Superviz.io
        </p>
        <div class="logos-grid">
          <span>Airbus</span><span>Thales</span><span>OVHcloud</span
          ><span>Scaleway</span><span>BlaBlaCar</span><span>Doctolib</span
          ><span>Datadog</span><span>Qonto</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12)">
          <h2>What our customers <span class="text-gradient">say</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonials-grid">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-quote">
              Superviz.io cut our incident response time by 60%. The anomaly
              detection catches issues our old monitoring completely missed.
              We've gone from 45-minute MTTR to under 15 minutes.
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="testimonial-avatar">ML</div>
              <div>
                <div class="testimonial-name">Marc Laurent</div>
                <div class="testimonial-role">VP Engineering, CloudScale</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-quote">
              We replaced three monitoring tools with Superviz.io. One dashboard,
              one agent, complete visibility. The ROI was immediate — we saved
              over &euro;40K per year on licensing alone.
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="testimonial-avatar">SD</div>
              <div>
                <div class="testimonial-name">Sarah Dubois</div>
                <div class="testimonial-role">SRE Lead, FinSecure</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-quote">
              The Kubernetes monitoring alone is worth it. Auto-discovers pods,
              tracks resource usage, alerts on OOM kills before they cascade.
              Our platform team finally sleeps at night.
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="testimonial-avatar">TN</div>
              <div>
                <div class="testimonial-name">Thomas Nguyen</div>
                <div class="testimonial-role">Platform Architect, DataFlow</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary)">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12)">
          <h2>Customer <span class="text-gradient">results</span></h2>
          <p class="subtitle subtitle-wide" style="margin-top: var(--space-4)">
            Real numbers from real teams using Superviz.io in production.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-metrics" style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto">
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-value">60%</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Faster MTTR</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-value">90%</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Less Alert Noise</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-value">3x</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Faster Root Cause</div>
          </div>
          <div class="metric">
            <div class="metric-value">99.9%</div>
            <div class="metric-label">Platform Uptime</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12)">
          <h2>Case <span class="text-gradient">studies</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="features-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="badge" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4)">SaaS</span>
            <h3>CloudScale reduced MTTR by 60%</h3>
            <p>
              CloudScale manages 2,000+ servers across three continents. After
              switching to Superviz.io, their mean time to resolution dropped
              from 45 minutes to under 15 minutes thanks to ML-powered anomaly
              detection and automated root-cause analysis.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--space-4)">
              <strong style="color: var(--text-primary)">Key result:</strong>
              60% reduction in MTTR, 40% fewer pages to on-call engineers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="badge" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4)">FinTech</span>
            <h3>FinSecure consolidated 3 tools into 1</h3>
            <p>
              FinSecure was paying for separate infrastructure monitoring, APM,
              and log management tools. Superviz.io replaced all three with a
              single platform, cutting costs by &euro;40K/year while improving
              visibility across their microservices architecture.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--space-4)">
              <strong style="color: var(--text-primary)">Key result:</strong>
              &euro;40K annual savings, single-pane-of-glass visibility.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="badge" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4)">Platform</span>
            <h3>DataFlow tamed Kubernetes chaos</h3>
            <p>
              DataFlow runs 500+ pods across 12 namespaces. Superviz.io's
              auto-discovery and resource tracking eliminated blind spots,
              catching OOM kills and resource contention before they caused
              cascading failures.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--space-4)">
              <strong style="color: var(--text-primary)">Key result:</strong>
              Zero cascading failures in 6 months, 30% resource optimization.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <span class="badge" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4)">Enterprise</span>
            <h3>Airbus standardized global monitoring</h3>
            <p>
              Airbus deployed Superviz.io across 50+ sites to create a unified
              monitoring standard. The SSO integration, RBAC controls, and audit
              logging met their stringent compliance requirements while giving
              teams real-time visibility.
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--space-4)">
              <strong style="color: var(--text-primary)">Key result:</strong>
              Unified monitoring across 50 sites, full compliance audit trail.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>
          Join thousands of teams using
          <span class="text-gradient">Superviz.io</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="subtitle subtitle-wide">
          Start monitoring for free. See results in minutes.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta" style="margin-top: var(--space-8)">
          <a href="pricing.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"
            >Start Free Trial &rarr;</a
          ><a href="contact.html" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg"
            >Request a Demo</a
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
